race.comment: BUCK SHINES (5) finished second (24.54) two back at Bendigo but out of the placings last time when 7th at Shepparton. Has ability and looks hard to stop. CALL IT FATE (2) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Missed the frame latest (26.00) when fifth over 450m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best figures. ATOMIC DIVA (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Bendigo following on from a second place finish (24.25) there the start prior. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Shapes as one to consider. SUNNY STRIDE (3) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this circuit.
